{"tid":680880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"的士直撼重型拖車尾部後被凌空彈起 司機胸及手腳受傷","createTime":"2018-05-27T13:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T14:09:22.000Z","uid":2547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a8c64a5d90a40e47606f445fdcbfb5623d67e571","tid":680880,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T13:55:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LbhdbvKAHhc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLbhdbvKAHhc&d=ULZlFYSNyvxZBbA0WolidttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=0f1fa6ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LbhdbvKAHhc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/215455_de2e65ebb47f015aef34c6b642c0a995.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F215455_de2e65ebb47f015aef34c6b642c0a995.jpg&h=a932b59e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/215455_a76450c14146f1f1375e8392d38100d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F215455_a76450c14146f1f1375e8392d38100d4.jpg&h=51283bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 青馬大橋往九龍方向，早前8時許，一輛雙層巴士因壞車停在慢線，青馬管制站3輛大小型工程及拖車及職員到場協助，其中重型拖車停距離現場約50米遠處，稍後一輛市區的士駛至，煞掣不及，直撼向拖車尾部，的士車頭嚴重損毀，司機胸及手腳受傷，由救護員送院治理，警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n讀者鄺先生提供影顯示，當時重型拖車頂及指揮均亮起閃燈警示，肇事的士從後駛至，並未見煞車燈亮起，直撼向重型拖車尾部，的士尾部撞至彈起再跌回地面，此時的士始亮起煞車燈號，惟車頭已撞至嚴重損毀。"},{"pid":"59bfa0a45fbb9598f43d41cf45b8ac49107c2505","tid":680880,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T14:05:53.000Z","msg":"樓市己死"},{"pid":"14527ba78d9ba48fe3b9fcc6a2a862040d4086c2","tid":680880,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T14:09:22.000Z","msg":"DC9 玩緊電話?"}]}